TS1                         1:45       2.0
TS1                         2:00       1.5
TS1                         2:15       1.0
TS1                         2:30       0.5
TS1                         2:45       0.2
TS1                         3:00       0.0

[REPORT]
;;Reporting Options
SUBCATCHMENTS ALL
NODES ALL
LINKS ALL

[TAGS]

[MAP]
DIMENSIONS 0.000 0.000 10000.000 10000.000
Units      None

